    "Geneva Bible": "1 His favor and the spirit of strength. 5:8 1 Or, masonry. 5:11 1 To wit, Solomon `[char_Solomon_Ref]`. [v_Ezr_1_1] 5:13 1 Read Ezra 1:1, 2. [v_Ezr_1_8] 5:14 1 Read Ezra 1:8. 5:17 1 Meaning, in the library, or places where lay the register or records of times."
